  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dde\u0d9b\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dba\u0da7 \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db1\u0ddc\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dba\u0ddd \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db0\u0dba\u0d9a",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Suva employees are protesting that they did not give the oil given for health",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A group of health workers staged a protest in front of the hospital against the Polonnaru Police and the employees of the Kaduruwela Cooperative Petrol Station claiming that the fuel given to the health workers of the Polonnaruwa General Hospital was not received properly.",
        "A large number of doctors and health workers of Polonnaru Hospital joined the protest against the injustice done by the police and the employees of the cooperative fuel station while providing fuel to the health workers.",
        "The health workers of the Polonnaruwa General Hospital say that the manager stole 2500 liters of petrol reserved for their health workers from the Kaduruwela Cooperative Petrol Station.",
        "The protestors also demanded that their health services be provided with enough fuel to run properly.",
        "Due to this protest by the doctors and health workers of the Polonnaruwa General Hospital, the patients who came to receive treatment from the Polonnaruwa General Hospital as well as the patients undergoing residential treatment were in dire straits."
      ],
